# Apex Digital Consultants — System Context

This document explains the **complete architecture and operational logic** of the Apex Digital Consultants platform.

It is intended for AI agents (Codex) and developers to understand how the system works before making changes.

The platform is a **modern marketing website combined with a lightweight CMS system** designed for Vercel serverless hosting.

---

# Platform Overview

The site serves two primary purposes:

1. A **premium marketing website** for Apex Digital Consultants
2. A **dynamic content management system** powering various sections of the site

Dynamic content includes:

- media assets
- portfolio items
- logos
- testimonials
- blog posts
- SEO landing pages

The platform is optimized for **low-cost serverless infrastructure**.

---

# Technology Stack

Frontend

- React
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Framer Motion

Backend

- Vercel serverless API routes

Database

